stadium development district; and
(B) by individuals who are not employees with respect to
income received for services performed in the territory
comprising the stadium development district;
for a particular state fiscal year; minus
(2) the income tax base period amount.
Sec. 11. As used in this chapter, "net increment" means the sum
of:
(1) the gross retail incremental amount; plus
(2) the income tax incremental amount;
as determined by the department of state revenue.
Sec. 12. As used in this chapter. "professional sports
development area" means the northwest Indiana professional
